sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant AuthCtrl as Auth Controller
    participant AuthSvc as Auth Service
    participant UserSvc as User Service
    participant OTPSvc as OTP Service
    participant TokenSvc as Token Service
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Email as Email Service

    U->>FE: Enter Email/Password
    FE->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>AuthCtrl: login

    AuthCtrl->>AuthSvc: validateLogin

    AuthSvc->>DB: FindOne user by email
    DB-->>AuthSvc: User document

    AuthSvc->>AuthSvc: Check account lock
    AuthSvc->>AuthSvc: Verify password

    alt Invalid Credentials
        AuthSvc-->>AuthCtrl: Authentication Error
        AuthSvc->>DB: Increment failed attempts
        AuthCtrl-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        FE-->>U: Show error
    else Valid Credentials
        AuthSvc->>DB: Reset failed attempts

        AuthSvc->>TokenSvc: createAccessToken
        TokenSvc-->>AuthSvc: JWT Access Token

        AuthSvc->>TokenSvc: createRefreshToken
        TokenSvc-->>AuthSvc: Refresh Token

        AuthSvc->>Redis: SET session:userId:deviceId
        Redis-->>AuthSvc: OK TTL=7 days

        AuthSvc->>UserSvc: updateUserLastLogin
        UserSvc->>DB: FindOneAndUpdate
        DB-->>UserSvc: Updated user

        AuthSvc-->>AuthCtrl: Return tokens
        AuthCtrl-->>FE: 200 OK + tokens
        FE-->>U: Navigate to Dashboard
    end

Note over U,Ext: Access Protected Route

    U->>FE: Access Protected Route
    FE->>API: GET /user/profile
    API->>AuthSvc: authenticate JWT

    alt Valid Token
        AuthSvc-->>API: Authenticated
        API->>UserSvc: getUserProfile
        UserSvc->>Redis: GET user:userId:profile
        Redis-->>UserSvc: Cache miss
        UserSvc->>DB: FindOne user
        DB-->>UserSvc: User data
        UserSvc->>Redis: SET user:userId:profile TTL=15min
        Redis-->>UserSvc: OK
        UserSvc-->>API: User profile
        API-->>FE: Profile data
        FE-->>U: Display profile
    else Invalid/Expired Token
        AuthSvc-->>API: Token Invalid
        API-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        FE->>API: POST /auth/refresh-token
        API->>TokenSvc: verifyRefreshToken
        TokenSvc->>Redis: GET session:userId
        Redis-->>TokenSvc: Valid session
        TokenSvc-->>API: New tokens
        API-->>FE: New access token
        FE->>API: GET /user/profile
    end

Note over U,Ext: Logout

    U->>FE: Logout
    FE->>API: POST /auth/logout
    API->>AuthSvc: logout
    AuthSvc->>Redis: DEL session:userId:*
    Redis-->>AuthSvc: OK
    AuthSvc->>TokenSvc: blacklistToken
    TokenSvc->>Redis: SET blacklisted:tokenId TTL=24h
    Redis-->>TokenSvc: OK
    AuthSvc-->>API: Logout success
    API-->>FE: 200 OK
    FE-->>U: Navigate to Login
